// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// docker-bake.hcl — Declarative build configuration for {{ project_name }}
//
// Requires: Docker Buildx (bundled with Docker Desktop / Docker Engine 23+)
//
// Usage:
//   docker buildx bake [group|target]       Build targets
//   docker buildx bake --print [target]     Preview build plan (dry-run)
//   docker buildx bake --list=targets       List available targets
//   docker buildx bake --list=variables     List available variables
//
// Examples:
//   docker buildx bake                      Build default (dev) targets
//   docker buildx bake prod                 Build all production targets
//   docker buildx bake app-prod             Build backend prod image only
//   TAG=v1.2.3 REGISTRY=ghcr.io/{{ github_username }} docker buildx bake prod
//
// Override any variable via environment:
//   TAG=abc123 docker buildx bake prod
//   REGISTRY=myregistry.azurecr.io docker buildx bake prod
//
// The companion docker-bake.override.hcl is auto-loaded for local dev.
// CI pipelines skip it via: docker buildx bake -f docker-bake.hcl [target]
// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

// ─── Variables ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

variable "TAG" {
  default     = "latest"
  description = "Image tag (semver, git SHA, 'latest')"
}

variable "REGISTRY" {
  default     = ""
  description = "Registry prefix (e.g. 'ghcr.io/{{ github_username }}'). Empty = local only."
}

variable "UV_VERSION" {
  default     = "0.10"
  description = "Astral UV version for Python dependency management"
}

variable "PLATFORM" {
  default     = ""
  description = "Target platform(s) — e.g. 'linux/amd64,linux/arm64'. Empty = native."
}

// ─── Functions ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

function "image_tags" {
  params = [name]
  result = notequal("", REGISTRY) ? [
    "${REGISTRY}/${name}:${TAG}",
  ] : [
    "${name}:${TAG}",
  ]
}

// ─── Groups ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

group "default" {
  targets = ["app-dev", "frontend-dev"]
}

group "dev" {
  targets = ["app-dev", "frontend-dev"]
}

group "prod" {
  targets = [
    "app-prod",
{%- if use_caddy %}
    "caddy",
{%- else %}
    "frontend-prod",
{%- endif %}
  ]
}

group "all" {
  targets = [
    "app-dev",
    "app-prod",
    "frontend-dev",
    "frontend-prod",
{%- if use_caddy %}
    "caddy",
{%- endif %}
  ]
}

// ─── Shared base targets (underscore prefix = not built directly) ────────────

target "_common" {
  labels = {
    "org.opencontainers.image.title"       = "{{ project_slug }}"
    "org.opencontainers.image.description"  = "{{ project_description }}"
    "org.opencontainers.image.authors"      = "{{ author_name }} <{{ author_email }}>"
    "org.opencontainers.image.source"       = "https://github.com/{{ github_username }}/{{ project_slug }}"
    "org.opencontainers.image.licenses"     = "{{ license }}"
    "org.opencontainers.image.version"      = "${TAG}"
  }
}

target "_prod" {
  inherits  = ["_common"]
  platforms = notequal("", PLATFORM) ? split(",", PLATFORM) : []
  attest = [
    { type = "provenance", mode = "max" },
    { type = "sbom" },
  ]
}

// ─── Backend (Python / FastAPI) ──────────────────────────────────────────────

target "app-dev" {
  description = "Backend dev image with hot-reload and dev dependencies"
  inherits    = ["_common"]
  context     = "."
  dockerfile  = "Containerfile"
  target      = "dev"
  tags        = image_tags("{{ project_slug }}-app")
  args = {
    UV_VERSION = UV_VERSION
  }
}

target "app-prod" {
  description = "Backend production image — minimal, non-root, health-checked"
  inherits    = ["_prod"]
  context     = "."
  dockerfile  = "Containerfile"
  target      = "prod"
  tags        = image_tags("{{ project_slug }}-app")
  args = {
    UV_VERSION = UV_VERSION
  }
}

// ─── Frontend (Vite / {{ frontend_framework | title }}) ──────────────────────

target "frontend-dev" {
  description = "Frontend dev image with HMR"
  inherits    = ["_common"]
  context     = "frontend"
  dockerfile  = "Containerfile"
  target      = "dev"
  tags        = image_tags("{{ project_slug }}-frontend")
}

target "frontend-prod" {
  description = "Frontend production image — optimized static assets"
  inherits    = ["_prod"]
  context     = "frontend"
  dockerfile  = "Containerfile"
  target      = "prod"
  tags        = image_tags("{{ project_slug }}-frontend")
}
{%- if use_caddy %}

// ─── Caddy (reverse proxy + frontend static assets) ──────────────────────────

target "caddy" {
  description = "Caddy reverse proxy with built-in frontend assets"
  inherits    = ["_prod"]
  context     = "."
  dockerfile  = "caddy/Containerfile"
  tags        = image_tags("{{ project_slug }}-caddy")
  args = {
    NODE_VERSION  = "{{ node_version }}"
    CADDY_VERSION = "2.9"
  }
}
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_celery %}

// ─── Celery (worker + beat — same image as app) ─────────────────────────────

target "worker-prod" {
  description = "Celery worker — uses the app-prod image"
  inherits    = ["app-prod"]
}
{%- endif %}
{%- if use_mcp %}

// ─── MCP Server ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

target "mcp-server-prod" {
  description = "MCP (Model Context Protocol) server"
  inherits    = ["app-prod"]
}
{%- endif %}
